  22"""Deserializing REST JSON payloads into an `aiobungie.crates` objects."""
  23
  24from __future__ import annotations
  25
  26__all__ = ("Factory", "EmptyFactory")

  59class Factory(interfaces.FactoryInterface):
  60    """The base deserialization factory class for all aiobungie objects.
  61
  62    This entity factory is used to deserialize JSON responses from the REST client and turning them
  63    into a `aiobungie.crates` Python classes.
  64    """
  65
  66    __slots__ = ("_net",)
  67
  68    def __init__(self, net: traits.Netrunner) -> None:
  69        self._net = net
  70
  71    def deserialize_bungie_user(self, data: typedefs.JSONObject) -> user.BungieUser:
  72        return user.BungieUser(
  73            id=int(data["membershipId"]),
  74            created_at=time.clean_date(data["firstAccess"]),
  75            name=data.get("cachedBungieGlobalDisplayName"),
  76            is_deleted=data["isDeleted"],
  77            about=data["about"],
  78            updated_at=time.clean_date(data["lastUpdate"]),
  79            psn_name=data.get("psnDisplayName", None),
  80            stadia_name=data.get("stadiaDisplayName", None),
  81            steam_name=data.get("steamDisplayName", None),
  82            twitch_name=data.get("twitchDisplayName", None),
  83            blizzard_name=data.get("blizzardDisplayName", None),
  84            status=data["statusText"],
  85            locale=data["locale"],
  86            picture=assets.Image(path=data["profilePicturePath"]),
  87            code=data.get("cachedBungieGlobalDisplayNameCode", None),
  88            unique_name=data.get("uniqueName", None),
  89            theme_id=int(data["profileTheme"]),
  90            show_activity=bool(data["showActivity"]),
  91            theme_name=data["profileThemeName"],
  92            display_title=data["userTitleDisplay"],
  93        )
  94
  95    def deserialize_partial_bungie_user(
  96        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
  97    ) -> user.PartialBungieUser:
  98        return user.PartialBungieUser(
  99            net=self._net,
 100            types=tuple(
 101                enums.MembershipType(type_)
 102                for type_ in payload.get("applicableMembershipTypes", ())
 103            ),
 104            name=payload.get("displayName"),
 105            id=int(payload["membershipId"]),
 106            crossave_override=enums.MembershipType(payload["crossSaveOverride"]),
 107            is_public=payload["isPublic"],
 108            icon=assets.Image(path=payload.get("iconPath", "")),
 109            type=enums.MembershipType(payload["membershipType"]),
 110        )
 111
 112    def deserialize_destiny_membership(
 113        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 114    ) -> user.DestinyMembership:
 115        name: str | None = None
 116        if (raw_name := payload.get("bungieGlobalDisplayName")) is not None:
 117            name = typedefs.unknown(raw_name)
 118
 119        return user.DestinyMembership(
 120            net=self._net,
 121            id=int(payload["membershipId"]),
 122            name=name,
 123            code=payload.get("bungieGlobalDisplayNameCode", None),
 124            last_seen_name=payload.get("LastSeenDisplayName")
 125            or payload.get("displayName")  # noqa: W503
 126            or "",  # noqa: W503
 127            type=enums.MembershipType(payload["membershipType"]),
 128            is_public=payload["isPublic"],
 129            crossave_override=enums.MembershipType(payload["crossSaveOverride"]),
 130            icon=assets.Image(path=payload.get("iconPath", "")),
 131            types=tuple(
 132                enums.MembershipType(type_)
 133                for type_ in payload.get("applicableMembershipTypes", ())
 134            ),
 135        )
 136
 137    def deserialize_destiny_memberships(
 138        self, data: typedefs.JSONArray
 139    ) -> collections.Sequence[user.DestinyMembership]:
 140        return tuple(
 141            self.deserialize_destiny_membership(membership) for membership in data
 142        )
 143
 144    def deserialize_user(self, data: typedefs.JSONObject) -> user.User:
 145        primary_membership_id: int | None = None
 146        if raw_primary_id := data.get("primaryMembershipId"):
 147            primary_membership_id = int(raw_primary_id)
 148
 149        return user.User(
 150            bungie_user=self.deserialize_bungie_user(data["bungieNetUser"]),
 151            memberships=self.deserialize_destiny_memberships(
 152                data["destinyMemberships"]
 153            ),
 154            primary_membership_id=primary_membership_id,
 155        )
 156
 157    def deserialize_searched_user(
 158        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 159    ) -> user.SearchableDestinyUser:
 160        code: int | None = None
 161        if raw_code := payload.get("bungieGlobalDisplayNameCode"):
 162            code = int(raw_code)
 163
 164        bungie_id: int | None = None
 165        if raw_bungie_id := payload.get("bungieNetMembershipId"):
 166            bungie_id = int(raw_bungie_id)
 167
 168        return user.SearchableDestinyUser(
 169            name=typedefs.unknown(payload["bungieGlobalDisplayName"]),
 170            code=code,
 171            bungie_id=bungie_id,
 172            memberships=self.deserialize_destiny_memberships(
 173                payload["destinyMemberships"]
 174            ),
 175        )
 176
 177    def deserialize_user_credentials(
 178        self, payload: typedefs.JSONArray
 179    ) -> collections.Sequence[user.UserCredentials]:
 180        return tuple(
 181            user.UserCredentials(
 182                type=enums.CredentialType(int(creds["credentialType"])),
 183                display_name=creds["credentialDisplayName"],
 184                is_public=creds["isPublic"],
 185                self_as_string=creds.get("credentialAsString"),
 186            )
 187            for creds in payload
 188        )
 189
 190    def deserialize_user_themes(
 191        self, payload: typedefs.JSONArray
 192    ) -> collections.Sequence[user.UserThemes]:
 193        return tuple(
 194            user.UserThemes(
 195                id=int(entry["userThemeId"]),
 196                name=entry["userThemeName"] if "userThemeName" in entry else None,
 197                description=entry["userThemeDescription"]
 198                if "userThemeDescription" in entry
 199                else None,
 200            )
 201            for entry in payload
 202        )

 204    def _deserialize_group_details(
 205        self,
 206        data: typedefs.JSONObject,
 207        current_user_memberships: collections.Mapping[str, clans.ClanMember]
 208        | None = None,
 209        clan_founder: clans.ClanMember | None = None,
 210    ) -> clans.Clan:
 211        features = data["features"]
 212        features_obj = clans.ClanFeatures(
 213            max_members=features["maximumMembers"],
 214            max_membership_types=features["maximumMembershipsOfGroupType"],
 215            capabilities=features["capabilities"],
 216            membership_types=features["membershipTypes"],
 217            invite_permissions=features["invitePermissionOverride"],
 218            update_banner_permissions=features["updateBannerPermissionOverride"],
 219            update_culture_permissions=features["updateCulturePermissionOverride"],
 220            join_level=features["joinLevel"],
 221        )
 222        information: typedefs.JSONObject = data["clanInfo"]
 223        progression: collections.Mapping[int, progressions.Progression] = {
 224            int(prog_hash): self.deserialize_progressions(prog)
 225            for prog_hash, prog in information["d2ClanProgressions"].items()
 226        }
 227
 228        return clans.Clan(
 229            net=self._net,
 230            id=int(data["groupId"]),
 231            name=data["name"],
 232            type=enums.GroupType(data["groupType"]),
 233            created_at=time.clean_date(data["creationDate"]),
 234            member_count=data["memberCount"],
 235            motto=data["motto"],
 236            about=data["about"],
 237            is_public=data["isPublic"],
 238            banner=assets.Image(path=data["bannerPath"]),
 239            avatar=assets.Image(path=data["avatarPath"]),
 240            tags=tuple(data["tags"]),
 241            features=features_obj,
 242            owner=clan_founder,
 243            progressions=progression,
 244            call_sign=information["clanCallsign"],
 245            banner_data=information["clanBannerData"],
 246            chat_security=data["chatSecurity"],
 247            conversation_id=int(data["conversationId"]),
 248            allow_chat=data["allowChat"],
 249            theme=data["theme"],
 250            current_user_membership=current_user_memberships,
 251        )
 252
 253    def deserialize_clan(self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject) -> clans.Clan:
 254        current_user_map: collections.Mapping[str, clans.ClanMember] | None = None
 255        if raw_current_user := payload.get("currentUserMemberMap"):
 256            # This will get populated if only it was a GroupsV2.GroupResponse.
 257            # GroupsV2.GetGroupsForMemberResponse doesn't have this field.
 258            current_user_map = {
 259                membership_type: self.deserialize_clan_member(membership)
 260                for membership_type, membership in raw_current_user.items()
 261            }
 262
 263        return self._deserialize_group_details(
 264            data=payload["detail"],
 265            clan_founder=self.deserialize_clan_member(payload["founder"]),
 266            current_user_memberships=current_user_map,
 267        )
 268
 269    def deserialize_clan_member(self, data: typedefs.JSONObject, /) -> clans.ClanMember:
 270        destiny_user = self.deserialize_destiny_membership(data["destinyUserInfo"])
 271        return clans.ClanMember(
 272            net=self._net,
 273            last_seen_name=destiny_user.last_seen_name,
 274            id=destiny_user.id,
 275            name=destiny_user.name,
 276            icon=destiny_user.icon,
 277            last_online=time.from_timestamp(int(data["lastOnlineStatusChange"])),
 278            group_id=int(data["groupId"]),
 279            joined_at=time.clean_date(data["joinDate"]),
 280            types=destiny_user.types,
 281            is_public=destiny_user.is_public,
 282            type=destiny_user.type,
 283            code=destiny_user.code,
 284            is_online=data["isOnline"],
 285            crossave_override=destiny_user.crossave_override,
 286            bungie_user=self.deserialize_partial_bungie_user(data["bungieNetUserInfo"])
 287            if "bungieNetUserInfo" in data
 288            else None,
 289            member_type=enums.ClanMemberType(int(data["memberType"])),
 290        )
 291
 292    def deserialize_clan_members(
 293        self, data: typedefs.JSONObject, /
 294    ) -> iterators.Iterator[clans.ClanMember]:
 295        return iterators.Iterator(
 296            self.deserialize_clan_member(member) for member in data["results"]
 297        )
 298
 299    def deserialize_group_member(
 300        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 301    ) -> clans.GroupMember:
 302        member = payload["member"]
 303        return clans.GroupMember(
 304            net=self._net,
 305            join_date=time.clean_date(member["joinDate"]),
 306            group_id=int(member["groupId"]),
 307            member_type=enums.ClanMemberType(member["memberType"]),
 308            is_online=member["isOnline"],
 309            last_online=time.from_timestamp(int(member["lastOnlineStatusChange"])),
 310            inactive_memberships=payload.get("areAllMembershipsInactive", None),
 311            member=self.deserialize_destiny_membership(member["destinyUserInfo"]),
 312            group=self._deserialize_group_details(payload["group"]),
 313        )
 314
 315    def _deserialize_clan_conversation(
 316        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 317    ) -> clans.ClanConversation:
 318        return clans.ClanConversation(
 319            net=self._net,
 320            id=int(payload["conversationId"]),
 321            group_id=int(payload["groupId"]),
 322            name=typedefs.unknown(payload["chatName"]),
 323            chat_enabled=payload["chatEnabled"],
 324            security=payload["chatSecurity"],
 325        )
 326
 327    def deserialize_clan_conversations(
 328        self, payload: typedefs.JSONArray
 329    ) -> collections.Sequence[clans.ClanConversation]:
 330        return tuple(self._deserialize_clan_conversation(conv) for conv in payload)

 345    def deserialize_app(self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject) -> application.Application:
 346        return application.Application(

 348            name=payload["name"],

 358    def _set_character_attrs(self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject) -> character.Character:
 359        return character.Character(
 360            net=self._net,
 361            id=int(payload["characterId"]),
 362            gender=enums.Gender(payload["genderType"]),
 363            race=enums.Race(payload["raceType"]),
 364            class_type=enums.Class(payload["classType"]),
 365            emblem=assets.Image(path=payload["emblemBackgroundPath"])
 366            if "emblemBackgroundPath" in payload
 367            else None,
 368            emblem_icon=assets.Image(path=payload["emblemPath"])
 369            if "emblemPath" in payload
 370            else None,
 371            emblem_hash=int(payload["emblemHash"]) if "emblemHash" in payload else None,
 372            last_played=time.clean_date(payload["dateLastPlayed"]),
 373            total_played_time=int(payload["minutesPlayedTotal"]),
 374            member_id=int(payload["membershipId"]),
 375            member_type=enums.MembershipType(payload["membershipType"]),
 376            level=payload["baseCharacterLevel"],
 377            title_hash=payload.get("titleRecordHash", None),
 378            light=payload["light"],
 379            stats={enums.Stat(int(k)): v for k, v in payload["stats"].items()},
 380        )

 382    def deserialize_profile(self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject, /) -> profile.Profile:
 383        payload = payload["data"]
 384        id = int(payload["userInfo"]["membershipId"])
 385        name = payload["userInfo"]["displayName"]
 386        is_public = payload["userInfo"]["isPublic"]
 387        type = enums.MembershipType(payload["userInfo"]["membershipType"])
 388        last_played = time.clean_date(payload["dateLastPlayed"])
 389        character_ids = tuple(int(cid) for cid in payload["characterIds"])
 390        power_cap = payload["currentSeasonRewardPowerCap"]
 391
 392        return profile.Profile(
 393            id=int(id),
 394            name=name,
 395            is_public=is_public,
 396            type=type,
 397            last_played=last_played,
 398            character_ids=character_ids,
 399            power_cap=power_cap,
 400            net=self._net,
 401        )
 402
 403    def deserialize_profile_item(
 404        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 405    ) -> profile.ProfileItemImpl:
 406        instance_id: int | None = None
 407        if raw_instance_id := payload.get("itemInstanceId"):
 408            instance_id = int(raw_instance_id)
 409
 410        version_number: int | None = None
 411        if raw_version := payload.get("versionNumber"):
 412            version_number = int(raw_version)
 413
 414        transfer_status = enums.TransferStatus(payload["transferStatus"])
 415
 416        return profile.ProfileItemImpl(
 417            net=self._net,
 418            hash=payload["itemHash"],
 419            quantity=payload["quantity"],
 420            bind_status=enums.ItemBindStatus(payload["bindStatus"]),
 421            location=enums.ItemLocation(payload["location"]),
 422            bucket=payload["bucketHash"],
 423            transfer_status=transfer_status,
 424            lockable=payload["lockable"],
 425            state=enums.ItemState(payload["state"]),
 426            dismantle_permissions=payload["dismantlePermission"],
 427            is_wrapper=payload["isWrapper"],
 428            instance_id=instance_id,
 429            version_number=version_number,
 430            ornament_id=payload.get("overrideStyleItemHash"),
 431        )
 432
 433    def deserialize_objectives(self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject) -> records.Objective:
 434        return records.Objective(
 435            net=self._net,
 436            hash=payload["objectiveHash"],
 437            visible=payload["visible"],
 438            complete=payload["complete"],
 439            completion_value=payload["completionValue"],
 440            progress=payload.get("progress"),
 441            destination_hash=payload.get("destinationHash"),
 442            activity_hash=payload.get("activityHash"),
 443        )

 445    # TODO: Remove **nodes and get it directly from the payload.
 446    def deserialize_records(
 447        self,
 448        payload: typedefs.JSONObject,
 449        scores: records.RecordScores | None = None,
 450        **nodes: int,
 451    ) -> records.Record:
 452        objectives: collections.Sequence[records.Objective] | None = None
 453        interval_objectives: collections.Sequence[records.Objective] | None = None
 454        record_state: records.RecordState | int
 455
 456        record_state = records.RecordState(payload["state"])
 457
 458        if raw_objs := payload.get("objectives"):
 459            objectives = tuple(self.deserialize_objectives(obj) for obj in raw_objs)
 460
 461        if raw_interval_objs := payload.get("intervalObjectives"):
 462            interval_objectives = tuple(
 463                self.deserialize_objectives(obj) for obj in raw_interval_objs
 464            )
 465
 466        return records.Record(
 467            scores=scores,
 468            categories_node_hash=nodes.get("categories_hash"),
 469            seals_node_hash=nodes.get("seals_hash"),
 470            state=record_state,
 471            objectives=objectives,
 472            interval_objectives=interval_objectives,
 473            redeemed_count=payload.get("intervalsRedeemedCount", 0),
 474            completion_times=payload.get("completedCount", None),
 475            reward_visibility=payload.get("rewardVisibility"),
 476        )
 477
 478    def deserialize_character_records(
 479        self,
 480        payload: typedefs.JSONObject,
 481        scores: records.RecordScores | None = None,
 482        record_hashes: collections.Sequence[int] = (),
 483    ) -> records.CharacterRecord:
 484        record = self.deserialize_records(payload, scores)
 485        return records.CharacterRecord(
 486            scores=scores,
 487            categories_node_hash=record.categories_node_hash,
 488            seals_node_hash=record.seals_node_hash,
 489            state=record.state,
 490            objectives=record.objectives,
 491            interval_objectives=record.interval_objectives,
 492            redeemed_count=payload.get("intervalsRedeemedCount", 0),
 493            completion_times=payload.get("completedCount"),
 494            reward_visibility=payload.get("rewardVisibility"),
 495            record_hashes=record_hashes,
 496        )

 498    def deserialize_character_dye(self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject) -> character.Dye:
 499        return character.Dye(
 500            channel_hash=payload["channelHash"], dye_hash=payload["dyeHash"]
 501        )

 503    def deserialize_character_customization(
 504        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 505    ) -> character.CustomizationOptions:
 506        return character.CustomizationOptions(
 507            personality=payload["personality"],
 508            face=payload["face"],
 509            skin_color=payload["skinColor"],
 510            lip_color=payload["lipColor"],
 511            eye_color=payload["eyeColor"],
 512            hair_colors=payload.get("hairColors", ()),
 513            feature_colors=payload.get("featureColors", ()),
 514            decal_color=payload["decalColor"],
 515            wear_helmet=payload["wearHelmet"],
 516            hair_index=payload["hairIndex"],
 517            feature_index=payload["featureIndex"],
 518            decal_index=payload["decalIndex"],
 519        )

 521    def deserialize_character_minimal_equipments(
 522        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 523    ) -> character.MinimalEquipments:
 524        if raw_dyes := payload.get("dyes"):
 525            dyes = tuple(self.deserialize_character_dye(dye) for dye in raw_dyes)
 526        else:
 527            dyes = ()
 528
 529        return character.MinimalEquipments(
 530            net=self._net, item_hash=payload["itemHash"], dyes=dyes
 531        )
 532
 533    def deserialize_character_render_data(
 534        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject, /
 535    ) -> character.RenderedData:
 536        return character.RenderedData(
 537            net=self._net,
 538            customization=self.deserialize_character_customization(
 539                payload["customization"]
 540            ),
 541            custom_dyes=tuple(
 542                self.deserialize_character_dye(dye)
 543                for dye in payload["customDyes"]
 544                if dye
 545            ),

 740    def deserialize_milestone(
 741        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 742    ) -> milestones.Milestone:
 743        start_date: datetime.datetime | None = None
 744        if raw_start_date := payload.get("startDate"):
 745            start_date = time.clean_date(raw_start_date)
 746
 747        end_date: datetime.datetime | None = None
 748        if raw_end_date := payload.get("endDate"):
 749            end_date = time.clean_date(raw_end_date)
 750
 751        rewards: collections.Collection[milestones.MilestoneReward] | None = None
 752        if raw_rewards := payload.get("rewards"):
 753            rewards = tuple(
 754                self._deserialize_milestone_rewards(reward) for reward in raw_rewards
 755            )
 756
 757        activities: collections.Sequence[milestones.MilestoneActivity] | None = None
 758        if raw_activities := payload.get("activities"):
 759            activities = tuple(
 760                self._deserialize_milestone_activity(active)
 761                for active in raw_activities
 762            )
 763
 764        quests: collections.Sequence[milestones.MilestoneQuest] | None = None
 765        if raw_quests := payload.get("availableQuests"):
 766            quests = tuple(
 767                self._deserialize_milestone_available_quest(quest)
 768                for quest in raw_quests
 769            )
 770
 771        vendors: collections.Sequence[milestones.MilestoneVendor] | None = None
 772        if raw_vendors := payload.get("vendors"):
 773            vendors = tuple(
 774                milestones.MilestoneVendor(
 775                    vendor_hash=vendor["vendorHash"],
 776                    preview_itemhash=vendor.get("previewItemHash"),
 777                )
 778                for vendor in raw_vendors
 779            )
 780
 781        return milestones.Milestone(
 782            hash=payload["milestoneHash"],
 783            start_date=start_date,
 784            end_date=end_date,
 785            order=payload["order"],
 786            rewards=rewards,
 787            available_quests=quests,
 788            activities=activities,
 789            vendors=vendors,
 790        )

 844    def deserialize_character_progressions(
 845        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 846    ) -> character.CharacterProgression:
 847        progressions_ = {
 848            int(prog_id): self.deserialize_progressions(prog)
 849            for prog_id, prog in payload["progressions"].items()
 850        }
 851
 852        factions = {
 853            int(faction_id): self._deserialize_factions(faction)
 854            for faction_id, faction in payload["factions"].items()
 855        }
 856
 857        milestones_ = {
 858            int(milestone_hash): self.deserialize_milestone(milestone)
 859            for milestone_hash, milestone in payload["milestones"].items()
 860        }
 861
 862        uninstanced_item_objectives = {
 863            int(item_hash): [self.deserialize_objectives(ins) for ins in obj]

 873                self._deserialize_artifact_tiers(tier) for tier in artifact["tiers"]
 874            ),
 875        )
 876        checklists = payload["checklists"]
 877
 878        return character.CharacterProgression(
 879            progressions=progressions_,
 880            factions=factions,
 881            checklists=checklists,
 882            milestones=milestones_,
 883            seasonal_artifact=seasonal_artifact,

 972    def deserialize_components(  # noqa: C901 Too complex.
 973        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 974    ) -> components.Component:
 975        # Due to how complex this method is, We'll stick to
 976        # typing.Optional here.
 977
 978        profile_: profile.Profile | None = None
 979        if raw_profile := payload.get("profile"):
 980            profile_ = self.deserialize_profile(raw_profile)
 981
 982        profile_progression: profile.ProfileProgression | None = None
 983        if raw_profile_progression := payload.get("profileProgression"):
 984            profile_progression = self.deserialize_profile_progression(
 985                raw_profile_progression
 986            )
 987
 988        profile_currencies: typing.Optional[
 989            collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]
 990        ] = None
 991        if raw_profile_currencies := payload.get("profileCurrencies"):
 992            if "data" in raw_profile_currencies:
 993                profile_currencies = self.deserialize_profile_items(
 994                    raw_profile_currencies["data"]
 995                )
 996
 997        profile_inventories: typing.Optional[
 998            collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]
 999        ] = None
1000        if raw_profile_inventories := payload.get("profileInventory"):
1001            if "data" in raw_profile_inventories:
1002                profile_inventories = self.deserialize_profile_items(
1003                    raw_profile_inventories["data"]
1004                )
1005
1006        profile_records: typing.Optional[
1007            collections.Mapping[int, records.Record]
1008        ] = None
1009
1010        if raw_profile_records_ := payload.get("profileRecords"):
1011            profile_records = self.deserialize_profile_records(raw_profile_records_)
1012
1013        characters: typing.Optional[
1014            collections.Mapping[int, character.Character]
1015        ] = None
1016        if raw_characters := payload.get("characters"):
1017            characters = self.deserialize_characters(raw_characters)
1018
1019        character_records: typing.Optional[
1020            collections.Mapping[int, records.CharacterRecord]
1021        ] = None
1022
1023        if raw_character_records := payload.get("characterRecords"):
1024            # Had to do it in two steps..
1025            to_update = {}
1026            for _, data in raw_character_records["data"].items():
1027                for record_id, record in data.items():
1028                    to_update[record_id] = record
1029
1030            character_records = {
1031                int(rec_id): self.deserialize_character_records(
1032                    rec, record_hashes=to_update.get("featuredRecordHashes", ())
1033                )
1034                for rec_id, rec in to_update["records"].items()
1035            }
1036
1037        character_equipments: typing.Optional[
1038            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]]
1039        ] = None
1040        if raw_character_equips := payload.get("characterEquipment"):
1041            character_equipments = self.deserialize_character_equipments(
1042                raw_character_equips
1043            )
1044
1045        character_inventories: typing.Optional[
1046            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]]
1047        ] = None
1048        if raw_character_inventories := payload.get("characterInventories"):
1049            if "data" in raw_character_inventories:
1050                character_inventories = self.deserialize_character_equipments(
1051                    raw_character_inventories
1052                )
1053
1054        character_activities: typing.Optional[
1055            collections.Mapping[int, activity.CharacterActivity]
1056        ] = None
1057        if raw_char_acts := payload.get("characterActivities"):
1058            character_activities = self.deserialize_character_activities(raw_char_acts)
1059
1060        character_render_data: typing.Optional[
1061            collections.Mapping[int, character.RenderedData]
1062        ] = None
1063        if raw_character_render_data := payload.get("characterRenderData"):
1064            character_render_data = self.deserialize_characters_render_data(
1065                raw_character_render_data
1066            )
1067
1068        character_progressions: typing.Optional[
1069            collections.Mapping[int, character.CharacterProgression]
1070        ] = None
1071
1072        if raw_character_progressions := payload.get("characterProgressions"):
1073            character_progressions = self.deserialize_character_progressions_mapping(
1074                raw_character_progressions
1075            )
1076
1077        profile_string_vars: typing.Optional[collections.Mapping[int, int]] = None
1078        if raw_profile_string_vars := payload.get("profileStringVariables"):
1079            profile_string_vars = raw_profile_string_vars["data"]["integerValuesByHash"]
1080
1081        character_string_vars: typing.Optional[
1082            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Mapping[int, int]]
1083        ] = None
1084        if raw_character_string_vars := payload.get("characterStringVariables"):
1085            character_string_vars = {
1086                int(char_id): data["integerValuesByHash"]
1087                for char_id, data in raw_character_string_vars["data"].items()
1088            }
1089
1090        metrics: typing.Optional[
1091            collections.Sequence[
1092                collections.Mapping[int, tuple[bool, records.Objective | None]]
1093            ]
1094        ] = None
1095        root_node_hash: int | None = None
1096
1097        if raw_metrics := payload.get("metrics"):
1098            root_node_hash = raw_metrics["data"]["metricsRootNodeHash"]
1099            metrics = tuple(
1100                {
1101                    int(metrics_hash): (
1102                        data["invisible"],
1103                        self.deserialize_objectives(data["objectiveProgress"])
1104                        if "objectiveProgress" in data
1105                        else None,
1106                    )
1107                }
1108                for metrics_hash, data in raw_metrics["data"]["metrics"].items()
1109            )
1110        transitory: fireteams.FireteamParty | None = None
1111        if raw_transitory := payload.get("profileTransitoryData"):
1112            if "data" in raw_transitory:
1113                transitory = self.deserialize_fireteam_party(raw_transitory["data"])
1114
1115        item_components: components.ItemsComponent | None = None
1116        if raw_item_components := payload.get("itemComponents"):
1117            item_components = self.deserialize_items_component(raw_item_components)
1118
1119        profile_plugsets: typing.Optional[
1120            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]]
1121        ] = None
1122
1123        if raw_profile_plugs := payload.get("profilePlugSets"):
1124            profile_plugsets = {
1125                int(index): [self.deserialize_plug_item_state(state) for state in data]
1126                for index, data in raw_profile_plugs["data"]["plugs"].items()
1127            }
1128
1129        character_plugsets: typing.Optional[
1130            collections.Mapping[
1131                int, collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]]
1132            ]
1133        ] = None
1134        if raw_char_plugsets := payload.get("characterPlugSets"):
1135            character_plugsets = {
1136                int(char_id): {
1137                    int(index): [
1138                        self.deserialize_plug_item_state(state) for state in data
1139                    ]
1140                    for index, data in inner["plugs"].items()
1141                }
1142                for char_id, inner in raw_char_plugsets["data"].items()
1143            }
1144
1145        character_collectibles: typing.Optional[
1146            collections.Mapping[int, items.Collectible]
1147        ] = None
1148        if raw_character_collectibles := payload.get("characterCollectibles"):
1149            character_collectibles = {
1150                int(char_id): self._deserialize_collectible(data)
1151                for char_id, data in raw_character_collectibles["data"].items()
1152            }
1153
1154        profile_collectibles: items.Collectible | None = None
1155        if raw_profile_collectibles := payload.get("profileCollectibles"):
1156            profile_collectibles = self._deserialize_collectible(
1157                raw_profile_collectibles["data"]
1158            )
1159
1160        profile_nodes: typing.Optional[collections.Mapping[int, records.Node]] = None
1161        if raw_profile_nodes := payload.get("profilePresentationNodes"):
1162            profile_nodes = {
1163                int(node_hash): self._deserialize_node(node)
1164                for node_hash, node in raw_profile_nodes["data"]["nodes"].items()
1165            }
1166
1167        character_nodes: typing.Optional[
1168            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Mapping[int, records.Node]]

1184                platform_silver = {

1186                    for platform_name, item in raw_platform_silver["data"][
1187                        "platformSilver"
1188                    ].items()
1189                }

1192            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.Currency]]

1198                    for char_id, currency in raw_char_lookups["data"].items()

1241    def deserialize_items_component(
1242        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
1243    ) -> components.ItemsComponent:
1244        # Due to how complex this method is, We'll stick to typing.Optional.
1245        instances: typing.Optional[
1246            collections.Sequence[collections.Mapping[int, items.ItemInstance]]
1247        ] = None
1248        if raw_instances := payload.get("instances"):
1249            instances = tuple(
1250                {int(ins_id): self.deserialize_instanced_item(item)}
1251                for ins_id, item in raw_instances["data"].items()
1252            )
1253
1254        render_data: typing.Optional[
1255            collections.Mapping[int, tuple[bool, dict[int, int]]]
1256        ] = None
1257        if raw_render_data := payload.get("renderData"):
1258            render_data = {
1259                int(ins_id): (data["useCustomDyes"], data["artRegions"])
1260                for ins_id, data in raw_render_data["data"].items()
1261            }
1262
1263        stats: typing.Optional[collections.Mapping[int, items.ItemStatsView]] = None
1264        if raw_stats := payload.get("stats"):
1265            stats = {}
1266            for ins_id, stat in raw_stats["data"].items():
1267                for _, items_ in stat.items():
1268                    stats[int(ins_id)] = self.deserialize_item_stats_view(items_)
1269
1270        sockets: typing.Optional[
1271            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.ItemSocket]]
1272        ] = None
1273        if raw_sockets := payload.get("sockets"):
1274            sockets = {
1275                int(ins_id): tuple(
1276                    self.deserialize_item_socket(socket) for socket in item["sockets"]
1277                )
1278                for ins_id, item in raw_sockets["data"].items()
1279            }
1280
1281        objectives: typing.Optional[
1282            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[records.Objective]]
1283        ] = None
1284        if raw_objectives := payload.get("objectives"):
1285            objectives = {
1286                int(ins_id): tuple(
1287                    self.deserialize_objectives(objective)
1288                    for objective in data["objectives"]
1289                )
1290                for ins_id, data in raw_objectives["data"].items()
1291            }
1292
1293        perks: typing.Optional[
1294            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Collection[items.ItemPerk]]
1295        ] = None
1296        if raw_perks := payload.get("perks"):
1297            perks = {
1298                int(ins_id): tuple(
1299                    self.deserialize_item_perk(perk) for perk in item["perks"]
1300                )
1301                for ins_id, item in raw_perks["data"].items()
1302            }
1303
1304        plug_states: typing.Optional[collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]] = None
1305        if raw_plug_states := payload.get("plugStates"):
1306            plug_states = tuple(
1307                self.deserialize_plug_item_state(plug)
1308                for _, plug in raw_plug_states["data"].items()
1309            )
1310
1311        reusable_plugs: typing.Optional[
1312            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]]
1313        ] = None
1314        if raw_re_plugs := payload.get("reusablePlugs"):
1315            reusable_plugs = {
1316                int(ins_id): tuple(
1317                    self.deserialize_plug_item_state(state) for state in inner
1318                )
1319                for ins_id, plug in raw_re_plugs["data"].items()
1320                for inner in tuple(plug["plugs"].values())
1321            }
1322
1323        plug_objectives: typing.Optional[
1324            collections.Mapping[
1325                int, collections.Mapping[int, collections.Collection[records.Objective]]
1326            ]
1327        ] = None
1328        if raw_plug_objectives := payload.get("plugObjectives"):
1329            plug_objectives = {
1330                int(ins_id): {
1331                    int(obj_hash): tuple(
1332                        self.deserialize_objectives(obj) for obj in objs
1333                    )
1334                    for obj_hash, objs in inner["objectivesPerPlug"].items()
1335                }
1336                for ins_id, inner in raw_plug_objectives["data"].items()
1337            }
1338
1339        return components.ItemsComponent(
1340            sockets=sockets,
1341            stats=stats,
1342            render_data=render_data,
1343            instances=instances,
1344            objectives=objectives,
1345            perks=perks,
1346            plug_states=plug_states,
1347            reusable_plugs=reusable_plugs,
1348            plug_objectives=plug_objectives,
1349        )

1736        payload: typedefs.JSONObject,
1737        /,
1738    ) -> activity.Activity:
1739        period = time.clean_date(payload["period"])
1740        details = payload["activityDetails"]
1741        ref_id = int(details["referenceId"])
1742        instance_id = int(details["instanceId"])
1743        mode = enums.GameMode(details["mode"])
1744        modes = tuple(enums.GameMode(int(mode_)) for mode_ in details["modes"])
1745        is_private = details["isPrivate"]
1746        membership_type = enums.MembershipType(int(details["membershipType"]))
1747
1748        # Since we're using the same fields for post activity method
1749        # this check is required since post activity doesn't values values
1750        values = self._deserialize_activity_values(payload["values"])
1751
1752        return activity.Activity(
1753            net=self._net,
1754            hash=ref_id,
1755            instance_id=instance_id,
1756            mode=mode,
1757            modes=modes,
1758            is_private=is_private,
1759            membership_type=membership_type,
1760            occurred_at=period,
1761            values=values,
1762        )

2319        breaker_type_hash: int | None = None
2320        if raw_break_type_hash := payload.get("breakerTypeHash"):
2321            breaker_type_hash = int(raw_break_type_hash)
2322
2323        energy: items.ItemEnergy | None = None
2324        if raw_energy := payload.get("energy"):
2325            energy = self.deserialize_item_energy(raw_energy)
2326
2327        primary_stats = None
2328        if raw_primary_stats := payload.get("primaryStat"):
2329            primary_stats = self.deserialize_item_stats_view(raw_primary_stats)
2330
2331        return items.ItemInstance(
2332            damage_type=enums.DamageType(int(payload["damageType"])),
2333            damage_type_hash=damage_type_hash,
2334            primary_stat=primary_stats,
2335            item_level=int(payload["itemLevel"]),
2336            quality=int(payload["quality"]),
2337            is_equipped=payload["isEquipped"],
2338            can_equip=payload["canEquip"],
2339            equip_required_level=int(payload["equipRequiredLevel"]),
2340            required_equip_unlock_hashes=required_hashes,
2341            cant_equip_reason=int(payload["cannotEquipReason"]),
2342            breaker_type=breaker_type,
2343            breaker_type_hash=breaker_type_hash,
2344            energy=energy,
2345        )

2419class EmptyFactory(Factory):
2420    """A stand-alone factory that doesn't requires a client instance.
2421
2422    # Example
2423    ---------
2424    ```py
2425    # We'll implement a serializable RESTClient.
2426    @dataclass(slots=True)
2427    class MyClient(aiobungie.traits.Serializable):
2428        rest = aiobungie.RESTClient(env["CLIENT_TOKEN"])
2429        my_name = "Fate"
2430        my_code = 4275
2431
2432        # Must implement this one method.
2433        @property
2434        def factory(self) -> aiobungie.EmptyFactory:
2435            # Return an empty factory
2436            return aiobungie.EmptyFactory()
2437
2438        async def my_memberships(self) -> Sequence[aiobungie.crates.DestinyMembership]:
2439            # Note, Do not call methods within objects, Since this is an empty
2440            # factory, The client reference that makes these calls will be `None`.
2441            response = await self.rest.fetch_membership(self.my_name, self.my_code)
2442            return self.factory.deserialize_destiny_memberships(response)
2443
2444
2445        async def main() -> None:
2446            client = MyClient()
2447            async with client.client:
2448                print(await client.my_memberships())
2449
2450    asyncio.run(main())
2451    ```
2452    """
2453
2454    __slots__ = ()
2455
2456    if typing.TYPE_CHECKING:
2457        # We explicitly want this to be `None`.
2458        _net: None
2459
2460    def __init__(self, net: None = None) -> None:
2461        self._net = net

 205    def _deserialize_group_details(
 206        self,
 207        data: typedefs.JSONObject,
 208        current_user_memberships: collections.Mapping[str, clans.ClanMember]
 209        | None = None,
 210        clan_founder: clans.ClanMember | None = None,
 211    ) -> clans.Clan:
 212        features = data["features"]
 213        features_obj = clans.ClanFeatures(
 214            max_members=features["maximumMembers"],
 215            max_membership_types=features["maximumMembershipsOfGroupType"],
 216            capabilities=features["capabilities"],
 217            membership_types=features["membershipTypes"],
 218            invite_permissions=features["invitePermissionOverride"],
 219            update_banner_permissions=features["updateBannerPermissionOverride"],
 220            update_culture_permissions=features["updateCulturePermissionOverride"],
 221            join_level=features["joinLevel"],
 222        )
 223        information: typedefs.JSONObject = data["clanInfo"]
 224        progression: collections.Mapping[int, progressions.Progression] = {
 225            int(prog_hash): self.deserialize_progressions(prog)
 226            for prog_hash, prog in information["d2ClanProgressions"].items()
 227        }

 230            net=self._net,
 231            id=int(data["groupId"]),
 232            name=data["name"],
 233            type=enums.GroupType(data["groupType"]),
 234            created_at=time.clean_date(data["creationDate"]),

 238            is_public=data["isPublic"],

 240            avatar=assets.Image(path=data["avatarPath"]),
 241            tags=tuple(data["tags"]),
 242            features=features_obj,
 243            owner=clan_founder,
 244            progressions=progression,
 245            call_sign=information["clanCallsign"],
 246            banner_data=information["clanBannerData"],
 247            chat_security=data["chatSecurity"],
 248            conversation_id=int(data["conversationId"]),
 249            allow_chat=data["allowChat"],

 251            current_user_membership=current_user_memberships,
 252        )

 254    def deserialize_clan(self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject) -> clans.Clan:
 255        current_user_map: collections.Mapping[str, clans.ClanMember] | None = None
 256        if raw_current_user := payload.get("currentUserMemberMap"):
 257            # This will get populated if only it was a GroupsV2.GroupResponse.
 258            # GroupsV2.GetGroupsForMemberResponse doesn't have this field.
 259            current_user_map = {
 260                membership_type: self.deserialize_clan_member(membership)
 261                for membership_type, membership in raw_current_user.items()
 262            }
 263
 264        return self._deserialize_group_details(
 265            data=payload["detail"],
 266            clan_founder=self.deserialize_clan_member(payload["founder"]),
 267            current_user_memberships=current_user_map,
 268        )

 447    def deserialize_records(
 448        self,
 449        payload: typedefs.JSONObject,
 450        scores: records.RecordScores | None = None,
 451        **nodes: int,
 452    ) -> records.Record:
 453        objectives: collections.Sequence[records.Objective] | None = None
 454        interval_objectives: collections.Sequence[records.Objective] | None = None
 455        record_state: records.RecordState | int
 456
 457        record_state = records.RecordState(payload["state"])
 458

 460            objectives = tuple(self.deserialize_objectives(obj) for obj in raw_objs)

 464                self.deserialize_objectives(obj) for obj in raw_interval_objs
 465            )
 466
 467        return records.Record(
 468            scores=scores,
 469            categories_node_hash=nodes.get("categories_hash"),
 470            seals_node_hash=nodes.get("seals_hash"),
 471            state=record_state,
 472            objectives=objectives,
 473            interval_objectives=interval_objectives,
 474            redeemed_count=payload.get("intervalsRedeemedCount", 0),
 475            completion_times=payload.get("completedCount", None),
 476            reward_visibility=payload.get("rewardVisibility"),

 741    def deserialize_milestone(
 742        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 743    ) -> milestones.Milestone:
 744        start_date: datetime.datetime | None = None
 745        if raw_start_date := payload.get("startDate"):
 746            start_date = time.clean_date(raw_start_date)
 747
 748        end_date: datetime.datetime | None = None
 749        if raw_end_date := payload.get("endDate"):
 750            end_date = time.clean_date(raw_end_date)
 751
 752        rewards: collections.Collection[milestones.MilestoneReward] | None = None
 753        if raw_rewards := payload.get("rewards"):
 754            rewards = tuple(
 755                self._deserialize_milestone_rewards(reward) for reward in raw_rewards
 756            )
 757
 758        activities: collections.Sequence[milestones.MilestoneActivity] | None = None
 759        if raw_activities := payload.get("activities"):
 760            activities = tuple(
 761                self._deserialize_milestone_activity(active)
 762                for active in raw_activities
 763            )
 764
 765        quests: collections.Sequence[milestones.MilestoneQuest] | None = None
 766        if raw_quests := payload.get("availableQuests"):
 767            quests = tuple(
 768                self._deserialize_milestone_available_quest(quest)
 769                for quest in raw_quests
 770            )
 771
 772        vendors: collections.Sequence[milestones.MilestoneVendor] | None = None
 773        if raw_vendors := payload.get("vendors"):
 774            vendors = tuple(
 775                milestones.MilestoneVendor(
 776                    vendor_hash=vendor["vendorHash"],
 777                    preview_itemhash=vendor.get("previewItemHash"),
 778                )
 779                for vendor in raw_vendors
 780            )
 781
 782        return milestones.Milestone(
 783            hash=payload["milestoneHash"],
 784            start_date=start_date,
 785            end_date=end_date,
 786            order=payload["order"],
 787            rewards=rewards,
 788            available_quests=quests,
 789            activities=activities,
 790            vendors=vendors,
 791        )

 845    def deserialize_character_progressions(
 846        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 847    ) -> character.CharacterProgression:
 848        progressions_ = {
 849            int(prog_id): self.deserialize_progressions(prog)
 850            for prog_id, prog in payload["progressions"].items()
 851        }
 852
 853        factions = {
 854            int(faction_id): self._deserialize_factions(faction)
 855            for faction_id, faction in payload["factions"].items()
 856        }
 857
 858        milestones_ = {
 859            int(milestone_hash): self.deserialize_milestone(milestone)

 875            ),
 876        )
 877        checklists = payload["checklists"]
 878
 879        return character.CharacterProgression(
 880            progressions=progressions_,
 881            factions=factions,
 882            checklists=checklists,
 883            milestones=milestones_,
 884            seasonal_artifact=seasonal_artifact,

 973    def deserialize_components(  # noqa: C901 Too complex.
 974        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
 975    ) -> components.Component:
 976        # Due to how complex this method is, We'll stick to
 977        # typing.Optional here.
 978
 979        profile_: profile.Profile | None = None
 980        if raw_profile := payload.get("profile"):
 981            profile_ = self.deserialize_profile(raw_profile)
 982
 983        profile_progression: profile.ProfileProgression | None = None
 984        if raw_profile_progression := payload.get("profileProgression"):
 985            profile_progression = self.deserialize_profile_progression(
 986                raw_profile_progression
 987            )
 988
 989        profile_currencies: typing.Optional[
 990            collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]
 991        ] = None
 992        if raw_profile_currencies := payload.get("profileCurrencies"):
 993            if "data" in raw_profile_currencies:
 994                profile_currencies = self.deserialize_profile_items(
 995                    raw_profile_currencies["data"]
 996                )
 997
 998        profile_inventories: typing.Optional[
 999            collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]
1000        ] = None
1001        if raw_profile_inventories := payload.get("profileInventory"):
1002            if "data" in raw_profile_inventories:
1003                profile_inventories = self.deserialize_profile_items(
1004                    raw_profile_inventories["data"]
1005                )
1006
1007        profile_records: typing.Optional[
1008            collections.Mapping[int, records.Record]
1009        ] = None
1010
1011        if raw_profile_records_ := payload.get("profileRecords"):
1012            profile_records = self.deserialize_profile_records(raw_profile_records_)
1013
1014        characters: typing.Optional[
1015            collections.Mapping[int, character.Character]
1016        ] = None
1017        if raw_characters := payload.get("characters"):
1018            characters = self.deserialize_characters(raw_characters)
1019
1020        character_records: typing.Optional[
1021            collections.Mapping[int, records.CharacterRecord]
1022        ] = None
1023
1024        if raw_character_records := payload.get("characterRecords"):
1025            # Had to do it in two steps..
1026            to_update = {}
1027            for _, data in raw_character_records["data"].items():
1028                for record_id, record in data.items():
1029                    to_update[record_id] = record
1030
1031            character_records = {
1032                int(rec_id): self.deserialize_character_records(
1033                    rec, record_hashes=to_update.get("featuredRecordHashes", ())
1034                )
1035                for rec_id, rec in to_update["records"].items()
1036            }
1037
1038        character_equipments: typing.Optional[
1039            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]]
1040        ] = None
1041        if raw_character_equips := payload.get("characterEquipment"):
1042            character_equipments = self.deserialize_character_equipments(
1043                raw_character_equips
1044            )
1045
1046        character_inventories: typing.Optional[
1047            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[profile.ProfileItemImpl]]
1048        ] = None
1049        if raw_character_inventories := payload.get("characterInventories"):
1050            if "data" in raw_character_inventories:
1051                character_inventories = self.deserialize_character_equipments(
1052                    raw_character_inventories
1053                )
1054
1055        character_activities: typing.Optional[
1056            collections.Mapping[int, activity.CharacterActivity]
1057        ] = None
1058        if raw_char_acts := payload.get("characterActivities"):
1059            character_activities = self.deserialize_character_activities(raw_char_acts)
1060
1061        character_render_data: typing.Optional[
1062            collections.Mapping[int, character.RenderedData]
1063        ] = None
1064        if raw_character_render_data := payload.get("characterRenderData"):
1065            character_render_data = self.deserialize_characters_render_data(
1066                raw_character_render_data
1067            )
1068
1069        character_progressions: typing.Optional[
1070            collections.Mapping[int, character.CharacterProgression]
1071        ] = None
1072
1073        if raw_character_progressions := payload.get("characterProgressions"):
1074            character_progressions = self.deserialize_character_progressions_mapping(
1075                raw_character_progressions
1076            )
1077
1078        profile_string_vars: typing.Optional[collections.Mapping[int, int]] = None
1079        if raw_profile_string_vars := payload.get("profileStringVariables"):
1080            profile_string_vars = raw_profile_string_vars["data"]["integerValuesByHash"]
1081
1082        character_string_vars: typing.Optional[
1083            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Mapping[int, int]]
1084        ] = None
1085        if raw_character_string_vars := payload.get("characterStringVariables"):
1086            character_string_vars = {
1087                int(char_id): data["integerValuesByHash"]
1088                for char_id, data in raw_character_string_vars["data"].items()
1089            }
1090
1091        metrics: typing.Optional[
1092            collections.Sequence[
1093                collections.Mapping[int, tuple[bool, records.Objective | None]]
1094            ]
1095        ] = None
1096        root_node_hash: int | None = None
1097
1098        if raw_metrics := payload.get("metrics"):
1099            root_node_hash = raw_metrics["data"]["metricsRootNodeHash"]
1100            metrics = tuple(
1101                {
1102                    int(metrics_hash): (
1103                        data["invisible"],
1104                        self.deserialize_objectives(data["objectiveProgress"])
1105                        if "objectiveProgress" in data
1106                        else None,
1107                    )
1108                }
1109                for metrics_hash, data in raw_metrics["data"]["metrics"].items()
1110            )
1111        transitory: fireteams.FireteamParty | None = None
1112        if raw_transitory := payload.get("profileTransitoryData"):
1113            if "data" in raw_transitory:
1114                transitory = self.deserialize_fireteam_party(raw_transitory["data"])
1115
1116        item_components: components.ItemsComponent | None = None
1117        if raw_item_components := payload.get("itemComponents"):
1118            item_components = self.deserialize_items_component(raw_item_components)
1119
1120        profile_plugsets: typing.Optional[
1121            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]]
1122        ] = None
1123
1124        if raw_profile_plugs := payload.get("profilePlugSets"):
1125            profile_plugsets = {
1126                int(index): [self.deserialize_plug_item_state(state) for state in data]
1127                for index, data in raw_profile_plugs["data"]["plugs"].items()
1128            }
1129
1130        character_plugsets: typing.Optional[
1131            collections.Mapping[
1132                int, collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]]
1133            ]
1134        ] = None
1135        if raw_char_plugsets := payload.get("characterPlugSets"):
1136            character_plugsets = {
1137                int(char_id): {
1138                    int(index): [
1139                        self.deserialize_plug_item_state(state) for state in data
1140                    ]
1141                    for index, data in inner["plugs"].items()
1142                }
1143                for char_id, inner in raw_char_plugsets["data"].items()
1144            }
1145
1146        character_collectibles: typing.Optional[
1147            collections.Mapping[int, items.Collectible]
1148        ] = None
1149        if raw_character_collectibles := payload.get("characterCollectibles"):
1150            character_collectibles = {
1151                int(char_id): self._deserialize_collectible(data)
1152                for char_id, data in raw_character_collectibles["data"].items()
1153            }

1156        if raw_profile_collectibles := payload.get("profileCollectibles"):
1157            profile_collectibles = self._deserialize_collectible(
1158                raw_profile_collectibles["data"]
1159            )

1162        if raw_profile_nodes := payload.get("profilePresentationNodes"):

1166            }

1172            character_nodes = {
1173                int(char_id): {
1174                    int(node_hash): self._deserialize_node(node)
1175                    for node_hash, node in each_character["nodes"].items()
1176                }

1178            }

1185                platform_silver = {

1242    def deserialize_items_component(
1243        self, payload: typedefs.JSONObject
1244    ) -> components.ItemsComponent:
1245        # Due to how complex this method is, We'll stick to typing.Optional.
1246        instances: typing.Optional[
1247            collections.Sequence[collections.Mapping[int, items.ItemInstance]]
1248        ] = None
1249        if raw_instances := payload.get("instances"):
1250            instances = tuple(
1251                {int(ins_id): self.deserialize_instanced_item(item)}
1252                for ins_id, item in raw_instances["data"].items()
1253            )
1254
1255        render_data: typing.Optional[
1256            collections.Mapping[int, tuple[bool, dict[int, int]]]
1257        ] = None
1258        if raw_render_data := payload.get("renderData"):
1259            render_data = {
1260                int(ins_id): (data["useCustomDyes"], data["artRegions"])
1261                for ins_id, data in raw_render_data["data"].items()
1262            }
1263
1264        stats: typing.Optional[collections.Mapping[int, items.ItemStatsView]] = None
1265        if raw_stats := payload.get("stats"):
1266            stats = {}
1267            for ins_id, stat in raw_stats["data"].items():
1268                for _, items_ in stat.items():
1269                    stats[int(ins_id)] = self.deserialize_item_stats_view(items_)
1270
1271        sockets: typing.Optional[
1272            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.ItemSocket]]
1273        ] = None
1274        if raw_sockets := payload.get("sockets"):
1275            sockets = {
1276                int(ins_id): tuple(
1277                    self.deserialize_item_socket(socket) for socket in item["sockets"]
1278                )
1279                for ins_id, item in raw_sockets["data"].items()
1280            }
1281
1282        objectives: typing.Optional[
1283            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[records.Objective]]
1284        ] = None
1285        if raw_objectives := payload.get("objectives"):
1286            objectives = {
1287                int(ins_id): tuple(
1288                    self.deserialize_objectives(objective)
1289                    for objective in data["objectives"]
1290                )
1291                for ins_id, data in raw_objectives["data"].items()
1292            }
1293
1294        perks: typing.Optional[
1295            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Collection[items.ItemPerk]]
1296        ] = None
1297        if raw_perks := payload.get("perks"):
1298            perks = {
1299                int(ins_id): tuple(
1300                    self.deserialize_item_perk(perk) for perk in item["perks"]
1301                )
1302                for ins_id, item in raw_perks["data"].items()
1303            }
1304
1305        plug_states: typing.Optional[collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]] = None
1306        if raw_plug_states := payload.get("plugStates"):
1307            plug_states = tuple(
1308                self.deserialize_plug_item_state(plug)
1309                for _, plug in raw_plug_states["data"].items()
1310            )
1311
1312        reusable_plugs: typing.Optional[
1313            collections.Mapping[int, collections.Sequence[items.PlugItemState]]
1314        ] = None
1315        if raw_re_plugs := payload.get("reusablePlugs"):
1316            reusable_plugs = {
1317                int(ins_id): tuple(
1318                    self.deserialize_plug_item_state(state) for state in inner
1319                )
1320                for ins_id, plug in raw_re_plugs["data"].items()
1321                for inner in tuple(plug["plugs"].values())
1322            }
1323
1324        plug_objectives: typing.Optional[
1325            collections.Mapping[
1326                int, collections.Mapping[int, collections.Collection[records.Objective]]
1327            ]
1328        ] = None
1329        if raw_plug_objectives := payload.get("plugObjectives"):
1330            plug_objectives = {
1331                int(ins_id): {
1332                    int(obj_hash): tuple(
1333                        self.deserialize_objectives(obj) for obj in objs
1334                    )
1335                    for obj_hash, objs in inner["objectivesPerPlug"].items()
1336                }
1337                for ins_id, inner in raw_plug_objectives["data"].items()
1338            }
1339
1340        return components.ItemsComponent(
1341            sockets=sockets,
1342            stats=stats,
1343            render_data=render_data,
1344            instances=instances,
1345            objectives=objectives,
1346            perks=perks,
1347            plug_states=plug_states,
1348            reusable_plugs=reusable_plugs,
1349            plug_objectives=plug_objectives,
1350        )
